<m:mi> t </m:mi>
<m:mi mathvariant="bold"> j </m:mi>
</m:math>
 in m/s. Find (i) acceleration and (ii) displacement at t = 1 s.
</para>
<para id="element-14"> <term>Solution : </term> Since velocity is given as a function in “t”, we can find acceleration by differentiating the function with respect to time.
</para>
<para id="element-12a">
