</para>
<para id="element-30"> <term>Solution : </term> Here, phrasing of question is important. We are required to find the rate of change of speed – not the rate of change of velocity or magnitude of rate of change of velocity. Let us have a look at the subtle differences in the meaning here :
</para>

<para id="element-33">
<term>1: </term> The rate of change of velocity
</para>
